data.description: A spacious one-story 3 BR TH in popular Halifax Plantation. Home has  a cozy front porch w/golf course view, 2014 LSF,  plus a private pool and spa. Home features luxury wood floors in living areas, tray ceilings,  plantation shutters and a 3-sided fireplace between large FR, bright and sunny LR and updated kitchen with ss appliances and large island with granite counters.  MBR has wood floors, ensuite bath with dbl vanities, tub and separate shower. Split floor plan has 2 guests rooms and full bath off LR/DR area.  The screened lanai features sitting area, summer kitchen and private pool with spa and waterfalls. Remote shades allow comfort and privacy 24/7.  Spacious 2 car garage is located off lanai with convenient back entrance. New roof - 2022.  Move in ready.  A must see!!
